      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW CORA (2) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Justified Jim (23.31) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Rates highly and will give a great sight. CAN'T IGNORE HER (7) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (22.95) at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Expected to feature again. DR. GIANNA (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at Sale over 435m behind Escaping Bindi (25.33) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Should play a prominent role. PAW VANNA (5) is right in the mix.",
